<div class="space-y-4">
<details class="group bg-transparent border-b border-border-light dark:border-border-dark fade-in-up">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer py-6 list-none text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        是否可以只預約單一妝髮服務？
                        <span class="transition group-open:rotate-45 text-xs">+</span>
</summary>
<div class="text-secondary-text dark:text-secondary-text-dark text-sm leading-relaxed pb-6 animate-fadeIn">
                        可按實際需求預約單一造型或全天跟妝服務，形式可靈活調整。
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-transparent border-b border-border-light dark:border-border-dark fade-in-up delay-100">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer py-6 list-none text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        是否提供伴娘或家人妝髮？
                        <span class="transition group-open:rotate-45 text-xs">+</span>
</summary>
<div class="text-secondary-text dark:text-secondary-text-dark text-sm leading-relaxed pb-6">
                        是的，我們提供親友妝髮服務，可以根據人數安排助理造型師協助。
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-transparent border-b border-border-light dark:border-border-dark fade-in-up delay-200">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer py-6 list-none text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        是否提供試妝服務？
                        <span class="transition group-open:rotate-45 text-xs">+</span>
</summary>
<div class="text-secondary-text dark:text-secondary-text-dark text-sm leading-relaxed pb-6">
                        提供試妝服務，需提前預約檔期。試妝費用可於正式服務中部分折抵。
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-transparent border-b border-border-light dark:border-border-dark fade-in-up delay-300">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer py-6 list-none text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        是否只服務普吉島地區？
                        <span class="transition group-open:rotate-45 text-xs">+</span>
</summary>
<div class="text-secondary-text dark:text-secondary-text-dark text-sm leading-relaxed pb-6">
                        主要服務普吉島全島，亦可接受泰國其他地區或海外出差邀約，差旅費用另計。
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-transparent border-b border-border-light dark:border-border-dark fade-in-up">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer py-6 list-none text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        建議提前多久預約？
                        <span class="transition group-open:rotate-45 text-xs">+</span>
</summary>
<div class="text-secondary-text dark:text-secondary-text-dark text-sm leading-relaxed pb-6">
                        建議至少提前 3-6 個月預約，旺季期間建議更早詢問以確保檔期。
                    </div>
</details>
